---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="A Narrative Lens | Digital Systems">
	<section class="space-y-12 py-20 animate-fade-in">
		<header class="space-y-4">
			<a href="/" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 mb-8">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" /></svg>
				Back Home
			</a>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-7xl font-display animate-slide-up">
				Digital <span class="text-gradient">Systems</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-2xl text-slate-400 font-display animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
				A Narrative Lens: Strategic Marketing for the Sovereign Entrepreneur.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white font-display">Freedom through Architecture</h2>
			<p>
				Most marketing "systems" are just traps—endless content treadmills that trade your time for vanity metrics. At A Narrative Lens, we architect systems that prioritize your <strong>Freedom</strong> and <strong>Integrity</strong>.
			</p>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-8">
				<div class="space-y-2">
					<div class="text-emerald-400 font-bold font-display text-lg">Grounded Strategy</div>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-400 text-balance">Sustainable growth that respects your capacity and storytelling.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-2">
					<div class="text-emerald-400 font-bold font-display text-lg">Agentic Systems</div>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-400 text-balance">Deploying AI and automation to handle the "noise" so you can focus on the signal.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-2">
					<div class="text-emerald-400 font-bold font-display text-lg">Sovereign Content</div>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-400 text-balance">Owning your platform, your data, and your relationship with your audience.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl space-y-6 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white font-display">The "Jamal 3.0" Approach</h3>
			<p class="text-slate-400">
				We don't just build websites; we build ecosystems. By merging technical enterprise-grade logic with artistic storytelling, we create brands that don't just exist—they resonate.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="flex justify-center pt-8">
			<a href="https://anarrativelens.com" class="btn-primary" style="background-color: #10b981; color: white;">Explore the Strategy</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
